### Get all deals
GET {{BASE_URL}}/deals

### Get a single deal by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/deals/1

### Create a new deal
POST {{BASE_URL}}/deals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Deal",
  "description": "Description for new deal"
}

### Update a deal by ID
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/deals/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Deal Name"
}

### Delete a deal by ID
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/deals/1